Package: tidynpi
Title: Efficient NPPES Provider Lookup via Parquet Lake and DuckDB
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Luis","MuÃ±oz Grass", role = c("aut","cre"),
           email = "luisfernando.mg21@gmail.com")
Description: Lookup, enrich, and match NPPES provider data via a hosted Parquet 
    snapshot accessible over HTTPS. Uses DuckDB for efficient columnar reads with 
    pushdown filters, Jaro-Winkler similarity for name matching, and provides 
    taxonomy code translation for human-readable provider specialties.
